Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:11.93,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}この身を捧げてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:17.16,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}沸き立つ思いを
